---
// Genres and Next section for the landing page
---
<section id="genres" class='py-20 px-4 animate-fade-in'>
  <div class='max-w-6xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center'>
    <div>
      <h2 class='text-3xl font-bold mb-4'>Para marcas y juegos que quieren <span class='text-brand-cyan'>visibilidad real</span></h2>
      <p class='text-text-muted mb-6'>Trabajamos con una amplia variedad de géneros y productos:</p>
      <div class='grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-center'>
        <div class='bg-brand-dark p-4 rounded-lg border border-brand-card col-span-2 flex items-center justify-center gap-2'>
          <svg class='w-5 h-5 text-brand-cyan' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2' viewBox='0 0 24 24'><path d='M12 4v16m8-8H4'></path></svg>
          Productos para Gamers
        </div>
        <div class='bg-brand-dark p-4 rounded-lg border border-brand-card flex items-center justify-center gap-2'>
          <svg class='w-5 h-5 text-brand-pink' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2' viewBox='0 0 24 24'><circle cx='12' cy='12' r='10'></circle></svg>
          Juegos Indie
        </div>
        <div class='bg-brand-dark p-4 rounded-lg border border-brand-card flex items-center justify-center gap-2'>
          <svg class='w-5 h-5 text-brand-purple' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2' viewBox='0 0 24 24'><rect x='4' y='4' width='16' height='16' rx='4'></rect></svg>
          RPG & Aventura
        </div>
        <div class='bg-brand-dark p-4 rounded-lg border border-brand-card flex items-center justify-center gap-2'>
          <svg class='w-5 h-5 text-brand-red' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2' viewBox='0 0 24 24'><polygon points='12,2 22,22 2,22'></polygon></svg>
          Estrategia
        </div>
        <div class='bg-brand-dark p-4 rounded-lg border border-brand-card flex items-center justify-center gap-2'>
          <svg class='w-5 h-5 text-brand-pink' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2' viewBox='0 0 24 24'><path d='M12 20v-6'></path><circle cx='12' cy='10' r='4'></circle></svg>
          Juegos de Terror
        </div>
        <div class='bg-brand-dark p-4 rounded-lg border border-brand-card col-span-2 flex items-center justify-center gap-2'>
          <svg class='w-5 h-5 text-brand-purple' fill='none' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='2' viewBox='0 0 24 24'><rect x='4' y='4' width='16' height='16' rx='4'></rect></svg>
          Marcas
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h3 class='text-2xl font-bold mb-4'>¿Qué sigue?</h3>
      <p class='text-text-muted'>
        Estamos en constante evolución para ofrecerte más. Próximamente expandiremos nuestra red a plataformas como <span class='text-text-light font-semibold'>TikTok</span> y <span
          class='text-text-light font-semibold'>YouTube</span
        >, además de incluir campañas para tu marca.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
